<section class="py-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-850">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
      고객들의 생생한 후기
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <% 3.times do |i| %>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-105">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <img class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full object-cover mr-4" src="https://source.unsplash.com/random/100x100/?person,face,<%= i %>" alt="User Avatar">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">사용자 <%= i + 1 %></p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">자동차 구매자</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            "CarPlatform 덕분에 꿈에 그리던 차량을 합리적인 가격에 구매할 수 있었습니다. 투명한 정보와 친절한 상담에 정말 감동했습니다!"
          </p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
